eu.play_project.dcep.distributedetalis.api

Interface DEtalisConfigApi

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DistributedEtalis

    public interface DEtalisConfigApi
    Set attributes used by a dEtalis instance. dEtalis can be configured with different implementations of an attribute. E.g. different output methods.
    Author:
    Stefan Obermeier
